## Notes:

- Render one image + link per option.
- Select the top 3 places.
- Each link should take the user to Google Maps.
- Send each image in succession (save in chat history); assign a number to each so the user can reference by their number.
- Create another agent to handle locations.

## Next Steps

Make everything work THE SAME in a Group chat.

Be precise and tell the agent to be super precise with the neighborhood.
